channel.title: Last time I logged on to runescape ever. | get my account
channel.description:
[b]So I haven't really player rs for years actually, just now and then when bored. But the last half year I didn't play at all anymore. Today I decided to log on...[/b] I walked into the G.E. and my chatbox gets overwhelmed by spammers, scamming dicers and doublers. On my way to the exchange desk or whatever it is I get 2 followers behind me. I stand still and my fear becomes reality. [i]player:"Can I have 100k please?" me:"You are level 17 what in god's name would you do with that money" player:"100k plzzzz i dance" me:"I don't give money away" player:"then give me a black (g) kiteshield" me:"I give u fucking nothing[/i] *Logs out to lobby and enter a new world* barely logged in and got another follower, a 37 this time. [i]player:"nice armour you got there" me:"how you mean its barely worth 10k it's just some hunter shit." player:"oh can i have it?" me:"you can't it's member armour" player:"can you buy me member?" me:"no I'm not even member myself anymore," player:"oh kk can I have 250k then?"[/i] *I though what the fucking hell, in my time they asked for 10gp not for 100 and 250k* [i]me: "why don't you work for it like everyone." player:"like what" me:"i dunno go mine and cut logs to get some capital and merchant or something" player:"Can't you just gimme 250k plzzzzz (mention the amount of z's) me:"[censored]"[/i] *walk into the GE crowd, drop the only 15m I had *Log out to never log back in Like seriously I can't even say the people evaluated looking to back when i was playing intensively. It's a whole new game, A shitty game, and I don't even mention the updates then. So I'm totally done with rs. Not that good but free so what more do you want. [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg27/scaled.php?server=27&filename=35976452.png&res=medium[/img] [img]http://desmond.imageshack.us/Himg267/scaled.php?server=267&filename=87011357.png&res=medium[/img] [img]http://img577.imageshack.us/img577/2492/81959580.png[/img] [b]How to get my account? [/b] easy just reply here :p I generated a number with http://www.random.org/ from 1 to 10, if you guess the right number you get my account. One entry/person Tomorrow around same time I posted this I will be giving the details to the winner (if there is one already) /inb4Everyoneonlysayingnumbers my post itself has value to! :| ps: I checked the rules if this was legit before some one says it ain't.
We do not allow the selling of accounts on this site. You may however give away accounts for free.
[b]Please give a thought on the situation I told and not just reply with a number D:[/b]
